subSections.title: Notes
subSections.text: ''{{w|Kangxi Dictionary}}'' recorded that this character is a variant of {{l|zh|荽}} per ''{{w|Yupian}}'' and ''{{w|Jiyun}}''. ''{{w|Hanyu Da Zidian}}'' did not include this sense and commented that the original referred character in both dictionaries is {{l|zh|䒘}}.
